[Another media report mentioned that the individual was a Chinese national who arrived on a flight with 14 Egyptians. The individual was asymptomatic, but specimens were taken. The 14 Egyptians are under quarantine and surveillance as well (see https://tinyurl.com/rvdgab2 in Arabic for more details. - Mod.MPP]

